msgid "It makes me happy to see you carry your cellphone around."
msgstr "携帯、持ち歩いてくれてて嬉しいよ。"

msgid "Because you're the one that got it for me?"
msgstr "ヒロが買ったものだから？"

msgid "That, but also..."
msgstr "うん、それもあるけど……"

msgid "...how to put this..."
msgstr "……なんて言ったらいいかな……"

msgid "It would be easy to forget it in a drawer if you don't have much use for it."
msgstr "あんまり使ってなかったら、簡単に引き出しの中とかに忘れちゃうはずでしょ。"

msgid "...At the very least, it makes for a good flashlight."
msgstr "……少なくとも、いい懐中電灯にはなるし。"

msgid "Right! What matters is that you carry it with you."
msgstr "だね！　大事なのは、持ち歩くことだから。"

msgid "Yeah."
msgstr "うん。"

msgid "You already have my number."
msgstr "僕の番号はもう登録してあるでしょ。"

msgid "Or are you showing me your wallpaper?"
msgstr "それとも、壁紙を見てほしいの？"

msgid "Look."
msgstr "見て。"

msgid "What's this?"
msgstr "これは？"

msgid "Apparently, it's my ticket back home."
msgstr "たぶん、帰りの切符になるもの。"

msgid "Really?"
msgstr "ホントに？"

msgid "If this ritual ends up working..."
msgstr "もし儀式がうまくいったら……"

msgid "(...And this doorknob isn't just some online scam...)"
msgstr "(……それに、このドアノブがただのネット詐欺じゃなかったら……)"

msgid "Then supposedly I can use this on a special door and it'll take me back home."
msgstr "特別な扉にこれを使えば、家に帰れることになってる。"

msgid "Really?!"
msgstr "ホントに!?"

msgid "Yeah, well, I wasn't going to do this ritual without a plan."
msgstr "うん、その、私も別に、無計画にこの儀式をしてるわけじゃないの。"

msgid "Thank goodness."
msgstr "よかった。"

msgid "All of my pestering worked."
msgstr "僕がしつこく言った甲斐があったね。"

msgid "Don't lose it!!"
msgstr "失くさないようにね!!"

msgid "Of course."
msgstr "もちろん。"

msgid "(This should reassure him a bit.)"
msgstr "(これで少しは安心してくれたはず。)"

msgid "(Reassurance complete. No need to bring this back up.)"
msgstr "(もう安心させ終わった。また見せる必要はない。)"

msgid "Are you going to try on makeup?"
msgstr "メイクをするの？"

msgid "Or maybe..."
msgstr "それとも……"

msgid "You want to put it on me???"
msgstr "僕に塗る気？？？"

msgid "...I was just showing you..."
msgstr "……見せてるだけ……"

msgid "Oh..."
msgstr "そっか……"

msgid "You sound almost... disappointed?"
msgstr "何かちょっと……がっかりしてない？"

msgid "Do you need help putting lipstick on?"
msgstr "塗るの、手伝ってあげようか？"

msgid "I-I'm not using it!"
msgstr "わ――私が塗るわけじゃないから！"

msgid "You do know that you're supposed to do that while the person is asleep, right?"
msgstr "そういうのは寝てる人にするものだよ。分かってるでしょ？"

msgid "You seemed so concentrated, I thought I could pull it off."
msgstr "すごく集中してたから、いけるかなと思って。"

msgid "I think I'll be locking my room tonight..."
msgstr "今夜は部屋に鍵をかけとくよ……"

msgid "Drawing on Hiro's face will have to wait."
msgstr "ヒロの顔に落書きするのはまた今度にしよう。"

msgid "Lace, I don't know what you're planning with that,"
msgstr "レイス、それで何をするつもりか知らないけど、"

msgid "but it's gonna be really hard to wash off."
msgstr "落とすのにかなり苦労するよ。"

msgid "Yeah... I'm aware."
msgstr "うん……わかってる。"

msgid "Um... do you need me to get up?"
msgstr "えっと……どいたほうがいい？"

msgid "Are you painting this bench?"
msgstr "このベンチを塗り替えるの？"

msgid "N-no... sorry."
msgstr "う――ううん……ごめん。"

msgid "Okay, turn around."
msgstr "わかった、後ろを向いて。"

msgid "...Huh?"
msgstr "……え？"

msgid "You don't want me to tie your hair with the ribbon?"
msgstr "そのリボンで髪を結んでほしいんでしょ？"

msgid "Oh! I forgot we used to do that."
msgstr "ああ！　確かに、前は結んでもらってたね。忘れてた。"

msgid "But I need it for something else, so no."
msgstr "でも、これは別のことに使うから、結ばなくていい。"

msgid "Bummer!"
msgstr "それは残念！"

msgid "Tying your hair will have to wait."
msgstr "髪を結ぶのはまた今度にしよう。"

msgid "...This is...?"
msgstr "……これは……？"

msgid "A rune, for the ritual."
msgstr "ルーン。儀式に使う。"

msgid "Oh... It's just a rock with a greek letter?"
msgstr "へぇ……ただの、ギリシャ文字が書かれた石？"

msgid "It's not greek, but yeah, more or less."
msgstr "ギリシャ文字じゃないけど、でもまあ、そんなところ。"

msgid "Interesting."
msgstr "興味深いね。"

msgid "No reason to show him again."
msgstr "もう一度見せる理由はない。"

msgid "The salt goes on the inside only..."
msgstr "塩をまくのは中だけでいい……"

msgid "Oh...? Lacie is learning to cook?"
msgstr "うん……？　料理の勉強かい？"

msgid "No, not yet."
msgstr "いや、まだ。"

msgid "Aww... It could've been fun!"
msgstr "えぇー……きっと楽しいのに！"

msgid "Maybe some other time."
msgstr "またいつかね。"

msgid "Hiro needs no further seasoning."
msgstr "これ以上ヒロに味付けする必要はない。"

msgid "My shoelaces! It's going to take ages to lace those back!"
msgstr "僕の靴紐！　元に戻すのに数世紀はかかるよ！"

msgid "I'm sorry, it's necessary."
msgstr "ごめん、必要なの。"

msgid "Those are my favorite, please don't lose them."
msgstr "お気に入りのやつだから、絶対失くさないでね。"

msgid "Lucky shoes? Or lucky shoelaces?"
msgstr "ラッキーシューズ？　それともラッキー靴紐？"

msgid "Lucky nothing if you lose them!!"
msgstr "失くしたらラッキー虚無だよ!!"

msgid "I'll be careful!"
msgstr "気を付ける！"

msgid "Here, take a look at them one last time."
msgstr "ほら、最後にもう一度だけ見ておいて。"

msgid "Whaaat?"
msgstr "最後ぉ？"

msgid "I have to burn them for the ritual."
msgstr "儀式で燃やさなきゃいけないから。"

msgid "Can't you use different ones?"
msgstr "別のじゃダメなの？"

msgid "They have to be red, and worn by a dummy."
msgstr "赤色で、アホが履いたやつじゃないといけないから。"

msgid "There's no way it says that..."
msgstr "絶対ウソでしょ……"

msgid "Let's not tease him anymore."
msgstr "もうからかうのはやめておこう。"

msgid "Are you learning how to sew?"
msgstr "裁縫の勉強かい？"

msgid "Not this year."
msgstr "今年はしない。"

msgid "I have a hole on this sweater you can practice on, you know."
msgstr "このセーターは穴が開いちゃってるから、練習に使えるよ。"

msgid "And risk damaging the kitty pattern even further?"
msgstr "子猫柄がいっそう崩れちゃうかもしれないよ？"

msgid "I believe in you!"
msgstr "レイシーを信じてるから！"

msgid "Make me a new sweater or something."
msgstr "新しいセーターか何かを作ってよ。"

msgid "This isn't yarn..."
msgstr "これ、毛糸じゃないから……"

msgid "Hiro isn't here."
msgstr "ヒロはいない。"

msgid "A nice bench, isolated from the public gaze."
msgstr "衆目から隔てられた、感じのいいベンチ。"

msgid "A bush."
msgstr "茂み。"

msgid "A nice chair."
msgstr "感じのいい椅子。"

msgid "Some pretty flowers are lined up on the sides."
msgstr "かわいらしい花が脇に並んで咲いている。"

msgid "A pond surrounded by flowers."
msgstr "花に囲まれた池。"

msgid "I wish we had frogs here."
msgstr "カエルがいたらよかったのに。"

msgid "Lamps that look a lot nicer at night."
msgstr "ランプ。夜はもっと雰囲気が良い。"

msgid "Another nice plant."
msgstr "ここにもいい感じの植物。"

msgid "Some pretty flowers."
msgstr "かわいらしい花。"

msgid "A potted plant. This one is called Jacques."
msgstr "鉢植え。名前はジャック。"

